## Third-Party Algorithm Dependency

This application uses `ts-fsrs` as the local FSRS scheduler implementation.

```text
package: ts-fsrs
version: 5.4.0
license: MIT
repository: https://github.com/open-spaced-repetition/ts-fsrs
```

Project rules:

```text
ts-fsrs version must be pinned exactly.
ReviewEvent records scheduler="ts-fsrs" and scheduler_version="5.4.0".
FSRS raw output is stored separately from product-adapted state.
The product rule "click word card = unfamiliar = browser_detail + again = add to today's review queue" is not represented as a raw FSRS daily review.
```

